---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Hiredesk">
  <div class="policy-page">
    <div class="container--smart">
      <header class="policy-header reveal">
        <h1 class="page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: March 29, 2026</p>
      </header>

      <div class="policy-content reveal">
        <section>
          <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
          <p>At Hiredesk ("we", "us", or "our"), our commitment to your privacy is absolute. This Privacy Policy details the types of personal data we collect, how it's utilized, and the robust measures we employ to keep your information secure in accordance with global standards.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>2. Information Collection</h2>
          <p>We collect information that you voluntarily provide to us when you express interest in our services, subscribe to our newsletters, or contact us through our digital platforms. This may include your name, business email, phone number, and organization details.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>3. Data Usage</h2>
          <p>Your information is used solely to deliver premium outsourcing solutions, streamline our communication, and enhance your overall experience with our brand. We do not sell or trade your personal information to third parties.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>4. Security Protocols</h2>
          <p>Hiredesk implements industry-leading cryptographic standards and administrative safeguards to protect your data from unauthorized access or disclosure. Our systems are regularly audited to ensure the highest levels of integrity.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You possess the right to access, rectify, or request the deletion of your personal data at any time. For such requests, please contact our data protection team via the methods listed below.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>6. Contact</h2>
          <p>Queries related to data privacy can be directed to: <br/><strong>privacy@hiredesk.com</strong></p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .policy-page {
    padding: 100px 0 60px;
    background-color: var(--bg-primary);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .container--smart {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .policy-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 4.2rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: #000;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .last-updated {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #666;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .policy-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .policy-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: #000;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .policy-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: #333;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
</style>
